<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1510759-does-anyone-knows-how-many-more-books-are">Does anyone knows how many more books are expected in the series? I love the books but i think it is time for Angie to be gone forever and for Will to finally get undisturbed HEA with Sara. He has suffered so much in his life he deserves to be happy. I am just terrified that Karin Slaughter will finish this series with him getting killed or ending up alone and miserable.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1510759'><a id="like_count_community_question_1510759" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1510759?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">14 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F42599605-the-last-widow">like</a></span>

