          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/43235896-the-last-widow">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/57073687-nadia?shelf=thriller">thriller</a>
